{"tid":660241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★預算案通過　最快6月中綜援出三糧兼補差額","createTime":"2018-05-10T13:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T13:55:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e1a0edef01dd3bfd8ee246d077838fa8aa754b","tid":660241,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"隨着立法會今日(10日)三讀通過《2018年撥款條例草案》，據了解，政府最快6月中向領取社會保障人士，包括綜援、高齡津貼、長者生活津貼等「出三糧」。因應政府補鑊推出派4000港元計劃，政府早前亦指現時社會保障受惠人士「出三糧」者，如領不足4000港元，會補回有關差額；據知共有43萬名社會保障人士受惠，涉及4.35億港元公帑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180510/bkn-20180510202616657-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180510%2Fbkn-20180510202616657-0510_00822_001.html&d=EkiJN8p3Xhrfj6Ct6vZ8nf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cd4a5aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180510/bkn-20180510202616657-0510_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"085c6d0e57000b21ef32263cb2d24a0f888a12e8","tid":660241,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"綜援又win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\npaid ffirst<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}